<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #f5f7fa; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); overflow: hidden; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ee4034 0%, #ee4034 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; }
        .header .code { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 10px; font-weight: 500; }
        .content { padding: 30px; }
        .greeting { font-size: 16px; color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .info-card { background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #ee4034; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px; }
        .info-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
        .info-table td { padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; }
        .info-table td:first-child { font-weight: 600; color: #495057; width: 140px; }
        .info-table td:nth-child(2) { width: 20px; color: #6c757d; }
        .info-table td:last-child { color: #2c3e50; }
        .cta-section { text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; }
        .btn { background: transparent; color: #ee4034; border: 2px solid #ee4034; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 25px; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block; transition: all 0.2s; }
        .btn:hover { background: #ee4034; color: white; transform: translateY(-2px); }
        .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; }
        .divider { height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ee4034, #ee4034); margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 1px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🎨 Request Design Revisi</h1>
            <div class="code"><%= data.trn_code_rd %></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Kepada Yth. <strong><%= kepada.user_name %></strong>
            </div>
            
            <p>Terdapat draft request desain yang direvisi oleh <%= oleh.user_name %>:</p>
            
            <div class="info-card">
                <table class="info-table">
                    <tr>
                        <td>📋 Project Title</td>
                        <td>:</td>
                        <td><strong><%= data.trn_project_title %></strong></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>👤 PIC Request</td>
                        <td>:</td>
                        <td><%= users.user_name %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>📅 Tanggal Target</td>
                        <td>:</td>
                        <td><%= target %></td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="<%= shortLink %>" class="btn">🚀 Klik disini</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>

            <p style="color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">
                Silakan klik tombol di atas untuk mengakses aplikasi Request Design dan melakukan proses approval.
                Jika ada pertanyaan, silakan hubungi tim terkait.
            </p>
            
            <p style="color: #2c3e50; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
                Regards,<br>
                <strong>Sistem Request Design</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            Copyright © 2026 IT DBC
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>